.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-LISTFORWARDS-FEE-AVG-MONTH" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-listforwards-fee-avg-month \- FEAT-2749 avg fee per forward in last 30d
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-listforwards-fee-avg-month
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reports the average fee per settled forward in the last 30 days (FEAT-2749).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN with key \fBavg_fee_msat_month\fR.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
